note over browser: 
The page  https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/spa as single page app.
The textfield has html attribute for name as note
The action and method attribute for form is not assigned.
Suppose we fill the textfield with text 'My new note' and press submit button
end note 

browser->server: Browser executes js code and send POST request to https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note_spa (with form data {content: 'My new note', date: '2020-04-06T18:20:46.394Z'})
server-->browser: Sends JSON response {"message":"note created"} with HTTP status code 201 ie. 201 status code means that a new note was created in server

note over browser:
browser executes js-code based on the server status 
appends the new list item to the existing lists
end note
